    <abstract id="aspace_39243e9e20f475ebd8b2aa5cf01e9b32">The Harrisville United Methodist Church (originally named the Methodist Episcopal Church of Harrisville) was formed in 1834 by Rev. William Carl. The records span the years 1875-1979. Combined church records make up the largest series and are concentrated around the years 1903-1967.</abstract>
